To install :
    first install ispell if necessary (http://ispell.sourceforge.net)

    make
    make install


the last version Available in 
     http://natura.di.uminho.pt/download/sources/Dictionaries/ispell/
or 
     http://linguateca.di.uminho.pt/dics/dics.html

